This folder contains the scripts to run the Genomic Evolutionary Rate Profiling (GERP) pipeline.

Requirements:
- python 3.8.10
- bedtools v2.29.1
- cactus v2.0.1+ as downloaded from https://github.com/ComparativeGenomicsToolkit/cactus
- PHAST software package as downloaded from http://compgen.cshl.edu/phast/
- maf_stream as downloaded from https://github.com/joelarmstrong/maf_stream
- GERP++ installed via conda (https://anaconda.org/bioconda/gerp)

